eTag.Description: Gets or sets the eTag for concurrency control.

location.Description: Gets or sets the Azure location in which migrate project is created.

properties.Description: Gets or sets the nested properties.

registeredTools.Description: Gets or sets the list of tools registered with the migrate project.

summary.Description: Gets the summary of the migrate project.

lastSummaryRefreshedTime.Description: Gets the last time the project summary was refreshed.

provisioningState.Description: Provisioning state of the migrate project.

refreshSummaryState.Description: Gets or sets the state of refresh summary.

lastSummaryRefreshedTime.Description: Gets or sets the time when summary was last refreshed.

extendedSummary.Description: Gets or sets the extended summary.

discoveredCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of entities discovered.

assessedCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of entities assessed.

replicatingCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of entities being replicated.

testMigratedCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of entities test migrated.

migratedCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of entities migrated.

etag.Description: Gets or sets the ETAG for optimistic concurrency control.

properties.Description: Gets or sets the properties of the solution.

tool.Description: Gets or sets the tool being used in the solution.

purpose.Description: Gets or sets the purpose of the solution.

goal.Description: Gets or sets the goal of the solution.

status.Description: Gets or sets the current status of the solution.

cleanupState.Description: Gets or sets the cleanup state of the solution.

summary.Description: Gets or sets the summary of the solution.

details.Description: Gets or sets the details of the solution.

databasesAssessedCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of databases assessed.

databaseInstancesAssessedCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of database instances assessed.

migrationReadyCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of databases ready for migration.

discoveredCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of servers discovered.

assessedCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of servers assessed.

replicatingCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of servers being replicated.

testMigratedCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of servers test migrated.

migratedCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of servers migrated.

groupCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of groups reported by the solution.

assessmentCount.Description: Gets or sets the count of assessments reported by the solution.

extendedDetails.Description: Gets or sets the extended details reported by the solution.
